                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gray-300 ml-auto group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16v1a3 3 0 003 3h10a3 3 0 003-3v-1m-4-4l-4 4m0 0l-4-4m4 4V4"/></svg>
                </a>
